title: VIDIV - Voice Insurance Verifier
description: Build a voice workflow for live dental insurance verification (PSTN → VAPI webhooks → FastAPI tools) with barge-in and concise TTS; will integrate real 270/271 eligibility.

title: Open-Source Dev Copilot
description: Built an assistant that only answers from trusted docs (pytorch.org/docs, docs.godotengine.org) and streams results step by step.

title: Heat Vulnerability & Cooling Access - San Diego County
description: Built a decision tool that prioritizes cooling-center locations by fusing satellite heat, demographics, and walkability.

title: Innovating for X (I4X) Internship - Father Joe's Villages
description: Built a location-aware platform for real-time resource coordination and staff-client communication in San Diego.

title: Recipe Overpromise Analytics
description: Can we detect, based on publish-time attributes, when a recipe author has overpromised and home cooks end up rating it poorly? Analyzed 83,782 Food.com recipes.
